#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Construction]
#title[Tangent bundle of abstract manifold]

We want to construct the analogue of the #local("009P")[tangent bundle] just for abstract manifolds this time.

Let $X$ be a #link("009D")[k-dimensional smooth manifold] with #local("0096")[atlas] $A$.
We define the _tangent bundle_ as the dijoint union of all tangent spaces.
$
  T M := U_(x in M) {x} xx T_(x) M
$

